The Company also plans to host an Investor Day Conference at its Minnetonka, Minnesota office on Wednesday, September 14, 2005 from 10:00 a.m. until 3:00 p.m. Central Time. Interested investors should email the Company at or call Investor Relations at 724-873-6788. Further Conference details will become available in the coming weeks.
