THE REORGANIZATION; SALE AND TRANSFER OF THE INTERESTS
     2.1 .
Reorganization of the Companies
          Prior to the Closing, Platinum shall cause a limited liability company to be formed under the laws of the State of Delaware ("") as an indirect wholly owned subsidiary of Platinum. Immediately prior to the Closing, Platinum shall take all necessary action to cause to be transferred to Seller the following (the ""):
