Effect of Termination
          If this Agreement is terminated as provided in , this Agreement shall be of no further force or effect; provided, however, that (i) this and and the Nondisclosure Agreement shall survive the termination of this Agreement and shall remain in full force and effect and (ii) the termination of this Agreement shall not relieve any party from any liability for fraud or from any liability for any breach of any representation, warranty, covenant, obligation or other provision contained in this Agreement giving rise to such termination.
