            (v)       no Participant (unless such Participant is an affiliate of such Lender, or is itself a Lender) shall be entitled to require such Lender to take or refrain from taking action under this Agreement or under any other Loan Document, except that such Lender may agree with such Participant that such Lender will not, without such Participant's consent, take action of the type described in subsections (a), (b), (c), (d), (e) or (f) of Section 10.03 hereof; notwithstanding the foregoing, in no event shall any participation by any Lender have the effect of releasing such Lenders from its obligations hereunder, and
